videos.title: Yahweh
videos.description: Yahweh is a song birthed from deep intimacy  with God, Yahweh  is a song of surrender-ness to God and His will, it tells how yielded we should be to God as His Saints.

videos.title: songs of the spirit
videos.description: Songs of the Spirit is a song birthed from intimacy with God Songs of the Spirit tells us how Great and Mighty God is and how the heavens worship Him day and night.

videos.title: Tobi Lo ba
videos.description: Tobi lo ba is a song that tells how good God his, Peace Iniolu is a minstrel whose mandate is to tell the world about the coming of the KING.

programmes.title: way keep
programmes.description: keep track of upcoming events that celebrate Peace's life. This includes events such as burial and wake keeping, where friends and loved ones can come together to pay their final respects and share memories. We believe that these events are an important way for us to come together as a community and remember Peace Iniolu Oba, and we hope that this section will help keep everyone informed and connected as we honor her life
